guide is a 1965 romantic drama film starring dev anand and waheeda rehman . it was directed by vijay anand , who contributed to the screenplay . the film is based on the novel the guide , by r. k. narayan . the film was a box office hit upon release . the movie proved memorable for its award-winning performances by the lead actors and memorable music by s. d. burman . time magazine listed it at number four on its list of best bollywood classics . a &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; u.s. version was written by pearl s. buck , and directed and produced by tad &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; . the film was screened at the 2007 cannes film festival , 42 years after its release .